<!-- Hero -->
<section id="hero">
  <h1>Visible Sound Systems</h1>
  <p>Reimagining live audio as both performance and art. Exceptional sound, bold design, and immersive community experiences inspired by cultural legends.</p>
  <a href="#about">Discover More</a>
</section>

<!-- About -->
<section id="about">
  <h2>About the Project</h2>
  <p>We build high-fidelity sound systems that merge technical excellence with sculptural design. Inspired by Caribbean dub systems and iconic performances like Pink Floyd Live at Pompeii, our mission is to bring the sound system back into focus—visually and sonically—at live events and venues across Europe.</p>
</section>

<!-- Technical -->
<section id="technical">
  <h2>Technical Innovation</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Speaker Construction</h3>
      <p>Cabinets of birch plywood, precision-braced for resonance control. Drivers optimized for frequency bands, paired with active DSP and Class D amplification for performance and reliability.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Acoustic Design</h3>
      <p>Modular, tunable enclosures ensure clear separation between lows, mids, and highs. Crossover points, delay alignment, and EQ tuned for immersive live experiences.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Finishing & Branding</h3>
      <p>Durable finishes, CNC-cut logos, and custom aesthetic elements integrate visual identity without compromising sound quality.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Design -->
<section id="design">
  <h2>Design Philosophy</h2>
  <p>Our systems are meant to be seen and felt. Bold geometric shapes, vibrant textures, and functional ergonomics combine to make the sound system an integral part of the live experience.</p>
</section>

<!-- Events & Community -->
<section id="events">
  <h2>Events & Community</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Launch Event</h3>
      <p>Flagship events in the Netherlands showcase our systems live. Attendees experience sound and design in perfect harmony.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Expansion</h3>
      <p>Following validation, we bring our events and systems to Madrid, London, and beyond, fostering community and brand presence across Europe.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Engagement</h3>
      <p>Through content, social media, and collaborations, we document and share our process, connecting with enthusiasts, designers, and music professionals.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

